product.title: Galaxy Hanging Neptune Gold-Plated Stud Earrings | NEW
product.body_html:
Pursue your dreams among the stars

A celestial masterpiece that brings the wonders of the universe to your style. These stud earrings are not only affordable but also a perfect gift for your partner, sister, or beloved mom, allowing them to shine with the beauty of the cosmos.

Each earring is a miniature work of art, featuring a stunning Neptune charm hanging gracefully from a radiant gold-plated stud. The intricate design captures the enchantment of the galaxy, making these earrings a symbol of infinite possibilities and dreams.

  • Shape: Neptune
  • Metal Type: Copper
  • Material: 18K Real Gold-Plating
  • Category: Earrings (Stud)
  • Package includes: 1 Pair of Earrings
  • Packaging: Earrings do not come with the original box to protect the environment but they do come in a plastic bag. Let's save our planet together from unnecessary waste.
  • Maintenance: 18k gold-plated jewelry will not fade. If the color becomes darker, wash it with soap to restore the brightness.

 

A wonderful gift for your loved ones

Dazzle the eyes but also prioritize comfort. Their lightweight design ensures you can wear them all day without any discomfort. These earrings are more than just a fashion statement; they are a symbol of inspiration and aspiration. 

Elevate your jewelry collection today with earrings from www.kawaiies.com!
